"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Required Node Configs\\n\\nThese configurations must be applied for both full nodes and validators.\\n\\n💡Note: failure to set up below configurations on a validator node may compromise chain functionality.\\n\\n## Node Configs\\n\\nThe dYdX Chain has important node configurations required for normal chain operation. This includes:\\n- The `config.toml` file read by CometBFT\\n  - ([Full documentation](https://docs.cometbft.com/v0.38/core/configuration))\\n- The `app.toml` file read by CosmosSDK\\n  - ([Full documentation](https://docs.cosmos.network/main/learn/advanced/config))\\n\\n### `config.toml`\\n\\n#### Consensus Configs\\n\\n```\\n[consensus]\\ntimeout_commit = \\\"500ms\\\"\\n```\\n\\n### `app.toml`\\n\\n#### Base Configuration\\n\\nReplace `$NATIVE_TOKEN_DENOM` at the end of the field with the correct value from [Network Constants](/nodes/network-constants)\\n```\\n### Gas Prices ###\\nminimum-gas-prices = \\\"0.025ibc/8E27BA2D5493AF5636760E354E46004562C46AB7EC0CC4C1CA14E9E20E2545B5,12500000000$NATIVE_TOKEN_DENOM\\\"\\n```\\n\\n```\\n### Pruning ###\\npruning = \\\"custom\\\"\\n\\n# Small numbers >= \\\"2\\\" for validator nodes.\\n# Larger numbers could be used for full-nodes if they are used for historical queries.\\npruning-keep-recent = \\\"7\\\"\\n\\n# Any prime number between \\\"13\\\" and \\\"97\\\", inclusive.\\npruning-interval = \\\"17\\\"\\n```\\n\\n#### gRPC Configs\\n\\n```\\n[grpc]\\n# Enable grpc. The Cosmos gRPC service is used by various daemon processes,\\n# and must be enabled in order for the protocol to operate:\\nenable = true\\n\\n# Non-standard gRPC ports are not supported at this time. Please run on port 9090, which is the default\\n# port specified in the config file.\\n# Note: grpc can be also be configured via start flags. Be careful not to change the default settings\\n# with either of the following flags: `--grpc.enable`, `--grpc.address`.\\naddress = \\\"0.0.0.0:9090\\\"\\n```\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs#required-node-configs\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>These configurations must be applied for both full nodes and validators.</p>\\n<p>💡Note: failure to set up below configurations on a validator node may compromise chain functionality.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs.mdx#required-node-configs\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nThese configurations must be applied for both full nodes and validators.\\n💡Note: failure to set up below configurations on a validator node may compromise chain functionality.\\n\",\"title\":\"Required Node Configs\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs#node-configs\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>The dYdX Chain has important node configurations required for normal chain operation. This includes:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>The <code>config.toml</code> file read by CometBFT\\n<ul>\\n<li>(<a href=\\\"https://docs.cometbft.com/v0.38/core/configuration\\\">Full documentation</a>)</li>\\n</ul>\\n</li>\\n<li>The <code>app.toml</code> file read by CosmosSDK\\n<ul>\\n<li>(<a href=\\\"https://docs.cosmos.network/main/learn/advanced/config\\\">Full documentation</a>)</li>\\n</ul>\\n</li>\\n</ul>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs.mdx#node-configs\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nThe dYdX Chain has important node configurations required for normal chain operation. This includes:\\n\\nThe config.toml file read by CometBFT\\n\\n(Full documentation)\\n\\n\\nThe app.toml file read by CosmosSDK\\n\\n(Full documentation)\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Node Configs\",\"titles\":[\"Required Node Configs\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs#configtoml\",\"html\":\"\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs.mdx#configtoml\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"config.toml\",\"titles\":[\"Required Node Configs\",\"Node Configs\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs#consensus-configs\",\"html\":\"\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;text-decoration:underline;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF;--shiki-dark-text-decoration:inherit\\\">consensus</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">timeout_commit = &quot;500ms&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs.mdx#consensus-configs\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n[consensus]\\ntimeout_commit = &quot;500ms&quot;\\n\",\"title\":\"Consensus Configs\",\"titles\":[\"Required Node Configs\",\"Node Configs\",\"config.toml\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs#apptoml\",\"html\":\"\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs.mdx#apptoml\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"app.toml\",\"titles\":[\"Required Node Configs\",\"Node Configs\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs#base-configuration\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Replace <code>$NATIVE_TOKEN_DENOM</code> at the end of the field with the correct value from <a href=\\\"/nodes/network-constants\\\">Network Constants</a></p>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\">### Gas Prices ###</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">minimum-gas-prices = &quot;0.025ibc/8E27BA2D5493AF5636760E354E46004562C46AB7EC0CC4C1CA14E9E20E2545B5,12500000000$NATIVE_TOKEN_DENOM&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\">### Pruning ###</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">pruning = &quot;custom&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\"># Small numbers &gt;= &quot;2&quot; for validator nodes.</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\"># Larger numbers could be used for full-nodes if they are used for historical queries.</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">pruning-keep-recent = &quot;7&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\"># Any prime number between &quot;13&quot; and &quot;97&quot;, inclusive.</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">pruning-interval = &quot;17&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs.mdx#base-configuration\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nReplace $NATIVE_TOKEN_DENOM at the end of the field with the correct value from Network Constants\\n### Gas Prices ###\\nminimum-gas-prices = &quot;0.025ibc/8E27BA2D5493AF5636760E354E46004562C46AB7EC0CC4C1CA14E9E20E2545B5,12500000000$NATIVE_TOKEN_DENOM&quot;\\n### Pruning ###\\npruning = &quot;custom&quot;\\n \\n# Small numbers &gt;= &quot;2&quot; for validator nodes.\\n# Larger numbers could be used for full-nodes if they are used for historical queries.\\npruning-keep-recent = &quot;7&quot;\\n \\n# Any prime number between &quot;13&quot; and &quot;97&quot;, inclusive.\\npruning-interval = &quot;17&quot;\\n\",\"title\":\"Base Configuration\",\"titles\":[\"Required Node Configs\",\"Node Configs\",\"app.toml\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs#grpc-configs\",\"html\":\"\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;text-decoration:underline;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF;--shiki-dark-text-decoration:inherit\\\">grpc</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\"># Enable grpc. The Cosmos gRPC service is used by various daemon processes,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\"># and must be enabled in order for the protocol to operate:</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">enable = true</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\"># Non-standard gRPC ports are not supported at this time. Please run on port 9090, which is the default</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\"># port specified in the config file.</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\"># Note: grpc can be also be configured via start flags. Be careful not to change the default settings</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\"># with either of the following flags: </span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\">`--grpc.enable`</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\">, </span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\">`--grpc.address`</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\\\">.</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">address = &quot;0.0.0.0:9090&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/running-node/required-node-configs.mdx#grpc-configs\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n[grpc]\\n# Enable grpc. The Cosmos gRPC service is used by various daemon processes,\\n# and must be enabled in order for the protocol to operate:\\nenable = true\\n \\n# Non-standard gRPC ports are not supported at this time. Please run on port 9090, which is the default\\n# port specified in the config file.\\n# Note: grpc can be also be configured via start flags. Be careful not to change the default settings\\n# with either of the following flags: `--grpc.enable`, `--grpc.address`.\\naddress = &quot;0.0.0.0:9090&quot;\",\"title\":\"gRPC Configs\",\"titles\":[\"Required Node Configs\",\"Node Configs\",\"app.toml\"]}]}}"
